@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pnzbnn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.32 * v0 + 0.62) + (v0 + 0.79 / v0 + 0.56)) / tmp)
    v0 = (0.28 - ((v2 + 0.26 * v0 + 0.02) / (v1 + 0.50 + v2 + 0.02)))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = v1
    tmp = (v1 / (0.03 - wp.sin(v2 + 0.68)))
    data[tid] = v0
